frontmatter.title: Why I don't like Gitflow?
frontmatter.metaKeywords: git, github, git flow, github flow, ship,feature flags, unleash, launch darkly
frontmatter.excerpt: While I'm sure it can probably be useful in certain situations, I don't like Gitflow and the ideas behind it. I think it's way too complex and that there are other easier solutions for a smoother workflow.
